---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { BOOKING_URL } from '../consts';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About | Granite State Tech Services"
  description="Meet Granite State Tech Services. Practical AI workshops, local SEO strategy, and conversion-focused websites for New Hampshire businesses."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Practical growth systems for local businesses.</h1>
    <p>
      Granite State Tech Services helps New Hampshire service businesses turn AI, SEO, and website
      traffic into booked calls. The focus is straightforward: fewer busywork hours, clearer funnels,
      and measurable revenue outcomes.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href={BOOKING_URL}>Book a consultation</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/blog">Read the playbooks</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="split">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">How I work</p>
      <h2>Built for operators, not theory.</h2>
      <p>
        Every engagement starts with one question: where is the current process leaking time,
        conversions, or search visibility? From there, we prioritize the fastest path to value.
      </p>
      <ul class="list">
        <li><span>01</span> Find the highest ROI workflow or funnel gap.</li>
        <li><span>02</span> Build repeatable systems your team can actually run.</li>
        <li><span>03</span> Track outcomes and iterate quickly.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="surface credibility-panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">What clients usually need</p>
      <ul class="list">
        <li><span>+</span> AI workshop rollout for real day-to-day tasks.</li>
        <li><span>+</span> Local SEO cleanup and service page strategy.</li>
        <li><span>+</span> Conversion-focused website refreshes.</li>
        <li><span>+</span> A clear 30/60/90 day execution plan.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="surface promise">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Working promise</p>
      <h2>Clear decisions, no fluff.</h2>
      <p>
        You get specific recommendations, scoped options, and concrete next steps. If something does
        not move toward measurable impact, it does not make the plan.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="promise-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href={BOOKING_URL}>Schedule a call</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:518-929-4295">Call 518-929-4295</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .credibility-panel {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .promise {
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    align-items: center;
  }

  .promise-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }
</style>
